\v 36 Unofambirei zvakadaro kushandura nzira yako, iwewo uchanyara neEgipita, sezvawakanyara neAsiriya.
\v 37 Hongu, uchabuda ubve pano, uye maoko ako ari pamusoro pemusoro wako, nokuti Jehovha wakaramba vaunovimba navo, newe haungabudiriri mazviri.
=======
